# Vercel serverless build uses the LEAN dependency set in requirements.txt
# (FastAPI/Uvicorn/Pydantic/Httpx/Tenacity/Apprise) so the function stays
# under the Python serverless size limit. The full dependency set
# (chromadb/langgraph/langchain/playwright/torch via pyproject.toml + uv.lock)
# is only for local dev and the Docker/Render container build, NOT for Vercel.
# Excluding these forces @vercel/python to fall back to requirements.txt.
uv.lock
pyproject.toml

# Local dev / debugging artifacts — never deploy these.
.venv_lean/
.venv/
*.log
_qip.py
.vercel/output/
